---
import BaseHead from '../../../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../../components/Footer.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from '../../../consts';
import FormattedDate from '../../../components/FormattedDate.astro';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title="Contributing & Helping - Zone Nova - GachaWiki" description="How to contribute to the Zone Nova wiki and help the community" />
		<style>
			main {
				width: 960px;
				margin: 0 auto;
				padding: 2rem 1rem;
				line-height: 1.6;
			}
			
			.breadcrumb {
				margin-bottom: 2rem;
				color: rgb(var(--gray));
			}
			
			.breadcrumb a {
				color: #8B4513;
				text-decoration: none;
			}
			
			.breadcrumb a:hover {
				text-decoration: underline;
			}
			
			.contribute-guide {
				background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
				border: 2px solid #8B4513;
				border-radius: 12px;
				padding: 2rem;
				box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
			}
			
			.page-header {
				text-align: center;
				margin-bottom: 3rem;
			}
			
			.page-title {
				font-size: 2.5rem;
				color: #8B4513;
				margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
				border-bottom: 3px solid #8B4513;
				padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
			}
			
			.page-subtitle {
				font-size: 1.1rem;
				color: rgb(var(--gray));
				margin: 0 0 2rem 0;
			}
			
			.contribute-guide h2 {
				color: #8B4513;
				font-size: 1.8rem;
				margin: 2rem 0 1rem 0;
				border-left: 4px solid #8B4513;
				padding-left: 1rem;
			}
			
			.contribute-guide h3 {
				color: #8B4513;
				font-size: 1.4rem;
				margin: 1.5rem 0 0.8rem 0;
			}
			
			.contribute-section {
				background: #f8f6f0;
				border: 2px solid #8B4513;
				border-radius: 8px;
				padding: 1.5rem;
				margin: 2rem 0;
			}
			
			.help-grid {
				display: grid;
				grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
				gap: 1.5rem;
				margin: 1rem 0;
			}
			
			.help-card {
				background: white;
				border: 1px solid #8B4513;
				border-radius: 8px;
				padding: 1.5rem;
			}
			
			.help-card h4 {
				color: #8B4513;
				font-size: 1.2rem;
				margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
			}
			
			.help-card ul {
				margin: 0;
				padding-left: 1rem;
			}
			
			.help-card li {
				margin: 0.5rem 0;
			}
			
			.contact-section {
				background: #e8f4f8;
				border: 2px solid #8B4513;
				border-radius: 8px;
				padding: 1.5rem;
				margin: 2rem 0;
				text-align: center;
			}
			
			.contact-section h3 {
				color: #8B4513;
				margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
			}
			
			.contact-button {
				background: #8B4513;
				color: white;
				padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
				border: none;
				border-radius: 8px;
				font-size: 1.1rem;
				text-decoration: none;
				display: inline-block;
				margin: 0.5rem;
				transition: 0.3s ease;
			}
			
			.contact-button:hover {
				background: #654321;
				transform: translateY(-2px);
			}
			
			.highlight-box {
				background: #fff3cd;
				border: 1px solid #ffc107;
				border-radius: 6px;
				padding: 1rem;
				margin: 1rem 0;
			}
			
			.highlight-box h4 {
				color: #856404;
				margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0;
			}
			
			.highlight-box p {
				margin: 0;
				color: #856404;
			}
			
			strong {
				color: #8B4513;
			}
			
			hr {
				border: none;
				border-top: 2px solid #8B4513;
				margin: 2rem 0;
			}
			
			@media (max-width: 720px) {
				main {
					padding: 1rem;
				}
				
				.contribute-guide {
					padding: 1.5rem;
				}
				
				.page-title {
					font-size: 2rem;
				}
				
				.help-grid {
					grid-template-columns: 1fr;
				}
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
			<!-- Breadcrumb -->
			<nav class="breadcrumb">
				<a href="/blog/">Blog</a> → 
				<a href="/blog/zone-nova/">Zone Nova</a> → 
				Contributing & Helping
			</nav>

			<!-- Contributing Guide Content -->
			<article class="contribute-guide">
				<!-- Page Header -->
				<header class="page-header">
					<h1 class="page-title">🤝 Contributing & Helping</h1>
					<p class="page-subtitle">Join our community and help make the Zone Nova wiki better for everyone</p>
				</header>

				<p>
					Welcome to the Zone Nova community! We're always looking for passionate players to help expand and 
					improve our wiki. Whether you're a veteran strategist or a newcomer with fresh insights, your 
					contributions are valuable and appreciated.
				</p>

				<h2>🎯 How to Contribute</h2>
				<div class="contribute-section">
					<p>
						Contributing to the Zone Nova wiki is easy and rewarding! We welcome all types of contributions, 
						from detailed character guides to quick corrections of outdated information.
					</p>
					
					<div class="highlight-box">
						<h4>🚀 Getting Started</h4>
						<p>
							The best way to contribute is to start with what you know best. Whether it's your favorite character, 
							a recent event you've mastered, or game mechanics you've figured out, your expertise helps everyone!
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>

				<h2>📝 What We Need Help With</h2>
				<div class="contribute-section">
					<div class="help-grid">
						<div class="help-card">
							<h4>⚔️ Character Guides & Builds</h4>
							<ul>
								<li>Detailed character reviews</li>
								<li>Optimal rune builds</li>
								<li>Team composition strategies</li>
								<li>Character tier rankings</li>
								<li>Skill rotation guides</li>
							</ul>
						</div>
						
						<div class="help-card">
							<h4>🎉 Event Walkthroughs</h4>
							<ul>
								<li>Step-by-step event guides</li>
								<li>Efficient farming strategies</li>
								<li>Event shop priority lists</li>
								<li>Boss battle tactics</li>
								<li>Time management tips</li>
							</ul>
						</div>
						
						<div class="help-card">
							<h4>📊 Tier List Updates</h4>
							<ul>
								<li>Current meta analysis</li>
								<li>Character rankings</li>
								<li>Equipment tier lists</li>
								<li>Team comp evaluations</li>
								<li>Balance change assessments</li>
							</ul>
						</div>
						
						<div class="help-card">
							<h4>🌐 Translation Work</h4>
							<ul>
								<li>Game announcement translations</li>
								<li>Patch note summaries</li>
								<li>Character story translations</li>
								<li>Event description translations</li>
								<li>Item description clarifications</li>
							</ul>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<hr>

				<h2>🛠️ How to Help</h2>
				<div class="contribute-section">
					<div class="contact-section">
						<h3>📢 Join Our Community</h3>
						<p style="margin-bottom: 1rem;">Ready to contribute? Here's how to get started:</p>
						<p><strong>Ask for access in YouTube channel or X .</strong></p>
						<a href="https://www.youtube.com/@GachaJunkie888" target="_blank" class="contact-button">🎥 YouTube Channel</a>
						<a href="https://x.com/EcchiPen" target="_blank" class="contact-button">🐦 X</a>
					</div>

					<h3>🎯 Ways You Can Help Right Now</h3>
					<div class="help-grid">
						<div class="help-card">
							<h4>📚 Share Your Knowledge</h4>
							<p>Have insights about character builds, team strategies, or game mechanics? Share them with the community!</p>
						</div>
						
						<div class="help-card">
							<h4>🔍 Report Outdated Information</h4>
							<p>Found information that's no longer accurate? Let us know so we can keep the wiki up to date!</p>
						</div>
						
						<div class="help-card">
							<h4>📸 Submit Screenshots & Guides</h4>
							<p>Visual guides are incredibly helpful! Share screenshots, infographics, or step-by-step visual guides.</p>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="highlight-box">
						<h4>💡 Quick Contribution Tips</h4>
						<p>
							<strong>Quality over quantity:</strong> Even small, accurate contributions are more valuable than lengthy but 
							incomplete guides. Start with what you know well and expand from there!
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>

				<hr>

				<h2>🌟 Community Guidelines</h2>
				<div class="contribute-section">
					<ul>
						<li><strong>Be Respectful:</strong> Treat all community members with kindness and respect</li>
						<li><strong>Stay Accurate:</strong> Verify information before sharing to maintain wiki quality</li>
						<li><strong>Give Credit:</strong> Acknowledge sources and other contributors when appropriate</li>
						<li><strong>Be Patient:</strong> Changes and updates may take time to review and implement</li>
						<li><strong>Have Fun:</strong> We're all here because we love Zone Nova - enjoy the process!</li>
					</ul>
				</div>

				<div class="contact-section">
					<h3>🎉 Thank You!</h3>
					<p>
						Every contribution, no matter how small, helps make the wiki better for all players. 
					</p>
				</div>
			</article>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html> 